*** AYENGEC DDR3 G2WA TEST PROJECT ***

Type HELP for menu

> help
================ DDR3 UART MENU ================

help                    : Print this detailed command menu.

mi                      : Show CAL and BUSY status bits.

mr AAAAAAAA             : Read one 32-bit word from address AAAAAAAA.

md AAAAAAAA LLLLLLLL    : Dump LLLLLLLL words from start address.

mw AAAAAAAA DDDDDDDD    : Write one 32-bit word DDDDDDDD.

mb AAAAAAAA LLLLLLLL PP : Block fill + verify for LLLLLLLL words.

bb LLLLLLLL PP          : Sweep 4 regions (0/32/64/96 MiB), fill + verify.

fa                      : Full 128 MiB test with default pattern PP=04.

fa PP                   : Full 128 MiB test with selected pattern code.

st                      : Print total RD/WR/ER and first error info.

clr                     : Clear all cumulative counters and error logs.

PP codes                : 00=ZERO 01=ONES 02=AAAA 03=5555 04=ADDR 05=LFSR.

Note                    : AAAAAAAA is a byte address, aligned to 4 bytes.

=================================================

